text: Falsamblesthis unguicularis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Tippmann in 1960. It is known from Bolivia.BioLib.cz - Falsamblesthis unguicularis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Forsteriini Category:Beetles described in 1960
title: Falsamblesthis unguicularis
